HEADWORD: Quadrijugous
<hw>Quad*rij"u*gous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>quadrijugus</ets> of a team of four; <ets>quattuor</ets> four +
<ets>jugum</ets> yoke.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Pinnate, with four
pairs of leaflets; <as>as, a <ex>quadrijugous</ex> leaf</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quadrilateral</ent>⟦br⟧
